n\n[02:25.97]I see my shame in the smoke\n[02:28.29]Every blessing got a bottle\n[02:30.29]Every prayer hits my throat\n[02:31.89]I been running on empty\n[02:33.33]But the shots still hit\n[02:34.77]I been laughing in public\n[02:36.61]Then I vanish so quick\n[02:37.57]Don’t call me strong\n[02:40.61]I’m just trained not to fold\n[02:43.09]Don’t call me lost\n[02:44.53]I just walk with this hole\n[02:46.77]And if tomorrow wants me\n[02:48.77]Tell tomorrow hold on\n[02:50.93]I’m under these drums\n[02:52.37]Trying to sway this storm\n[02:57.65]Drink\n[02:57.81]Drink\n[02:57.89]Baby, let it go\n[03:01.17]Drink\n[03:01.41]Drink\n[03:01.73]There’s a better road\n[03:04.69]Don’t save me now\n[03:05.81]Don’t save me now\n[03:07.15]Don’t save me now\n[03:18.21]Drink\n[03:28.37]Drink\n[03:28.69]Drink\n[03:28.85]Drink\n[03:28.85]Drink\n[03:28.85]Drink\n[03:28.85]Drink\n[03:28.85]Drink\n[03:28.85]Drink, drink, drink, drink\n[03:28.85]Drink, drink, drink, drink\n[03:53.49]Drink, drink, drink, drink\n[03:53.49]I don’t wanna feel tonight\n[04:01.73]Drink, drink, drink, drink\n[04:03.73]Put my sorrow in the light\n[04:03.73]Drink, drink, drink, drink\n[04:04.05]Bottle glowing by my bed\n[04:04.05]Drink, drink, drink, drink\n[04:04.05]Pain keeps pounding in my head\n[04:04.08]Drink\n[04:04.09]Drink\n[04:04.09]Drink\n[04:04.10]Drink\n[04:04.11]Don’t save me\n[04:04.12]Don’t save me\n[04:04.64]Don’t save me now\n"
